  "texts": [
    "The annotation of traits to the essays depends on the essay type.",
    "In the AES dataset, there are three essay types but the argumentative and narrative essays share the same type of trait sets.",
    "Thus, the essay sets of traits are divided into two, namely traits of argumentative or persuasive essays and attributes for source-dependent responses.",
    "The traits for the argumentative or persuasive essays are content, organization, word choice, sentence fluency, and conventions whereas for the source-dependent essays the traits are content, prompt adherence, language, and narrativeness.",
    "Hub presented Korean language essay writing evaluation dataset 3 that consists 50 topics and 50,413 cases."
  ],
